{"tid":2094861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英國有邊個地方少人又岩我地建立’小香港‘","createTime":"2020-07-05T04:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T05:48:09.000Z","uid":105176,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d131e9f08e33df22a70ff5115171ae3d81204d77","tid":2094861,"uid":105176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:23:12.000Z","msg":"如果我地想保留香港文化 應該要有個地方係以香港人為主要群體 <br />\n<br />\n但係唔好誤會我意思 香港人當然要融入本地圈子 唔好喂喂喂 只係我希望有一個地方香港人會集中少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5fce77651751e7dd0b80838ec6e76ebd8b1d21","tid":2094861,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:24:55.000Z","msg":"英國好多地方冇人住，同英國人傾好應該冇咩問題"},{"pid":"3784544f8494f7cf9650a454599c6c66d59d983d","tid":2094861,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:27:02.000Z","msg":"Torquay"},{"pid":"aa0079813f9b67192a614082b869e9c1ca51d1c3","tid":2094861,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:31:30.000Z","msg":"搭單想講<br />\n想發展香港嘅體育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想有隊波叫HongKongese而唔關香港政府事"},{"pid":"023d35d2d16b71535be389d84594fee4885b9ef8","tid":2094861,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:33:01.000Z","msg":"新界"},{"pid":"85adc59c144fa33df4bd2aa0b8f71770a666aa20","tid":2094861,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:33:24.000Z","msg":"直布羅陀"},{"pid":"9329fd3bb6bc33a9fdf2e2641747ed097c52597e","tid":2094861,"uid":43663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:35:13.000Z","msg":"New Hongkong, UK? 過多50 年咪又會叫獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />融入其他族群或者守護我城啦"},{"pid":"fac7b7456f57706c19f4e1b728e2e1aacbbe64e2","tid":2094861,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa0079813f9b67192a614082b869e9c1ca51d1c3","tid":2094861,"uid":199893,"like":